query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.accountStatus, u.createdAt, m.id as member_id 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN members m ON u.id = m.userId 
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Test%' OR u.name LIKE '%test%' OR u.name LIKE '%Emma Wilson%'
ORDER BY u.createdAt DESC;
